[00:30.10]	As far as toucheth my particular,
[00:32.92]	Yet, dread Priam,
[00:34.51]	There is no lady of more softer bowels,
[00:37.76]	More spongy to suck in the sense of fear,
[00:41.17]	More ready to cry out 'Who knows what follows?'
[00:44.86]	Than Hector is: the wound of peace is surety,
[00:48.47]	Surety secure; but modest doubt is call'd
